ADVERTENCIA!

Risk of injury due to patient falling out of bed!  Ensure that folded-up side rails are securely anchored.  Press against side rails from inside in order to check stability.  Hospital personnel are responsible for ensuring side rails are folded-up when the bed is occupied.

